Burnley are making an improved £3m offer for West Bromwich Albion defender Craig Dawson.

The 24-year-old Rochdale-born centre-back is keen to link up with Sean Dyche as he believes he will get a regular run in the side and has asked to leave.

Burnley are also keen on Nathaniel Chalobah at Chelsea and will ask to take the 19-year-old on loan.

